00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:49.580
BILL MOTE: The AsyncTask went
from being single threaded to

00:01:49.580 --> 00:01:51.630
then being parallel
processed and then

00:01:51.630 --> 00:01:52.710
back to single threaded.

00:01:52.710 --> 00:01:55.150
